==露天性爱==
近年来，卡尔顿山作为[[公開性行為|露天性爱]]的场所变得臭名昭著。随着吸毒者和未成年饮酒者的到来，男性之间的[[性交易|卖淫]]正在增加。在爱丁堡，这一地区是传统的同性性行为场所<ref>McLaughlin, Mark. [http://edinburghnews.scotsman.com/edinburghssexindustry/Calton-Hill-39rent-boys39-move.3677172.jp "Calton Hill 'rent boys' move trade into residential streets"] {{Wayback|url=http://edinburghnews.scotsman.com/edinburghssexindustry/Calton-Hill-39rent-boys39-move.3677172.jp |date=20110615124328 }}. ''The Scotsman'' 16 Jan 2008</ref>。在一个不名譽的事件中，一名男子因在山脚下用[[交通錐|交通錐]]刺激自己而被捕<ref>[http://edinburghnews.scotsman.com/weirdoddandquirkystories/Police-charge-man-over-sex.2358479.jp "Police charge man over sex with traffic cone"] {{Wayback|url=http://edinburghnews.scotsman.com/weirdoddandquirkystories/Police-charge-man-over-sex.2358479.jp |date=20110615124425 }}. ''The Scotsman'' 5 Sept 2002</ref>。

==活动==
[[File:Beltane_on_Calton_Hill_by_Bruce_McAdam.jpg|thumb]]
一年中，在卡尔顿山会举办许多活动，其中规模最大的是每年4月30日举行的五朔节（Beltane Fire Festival），有12,000人参加。这是古代凯尔特五朔节在卡尔顿山的复兴<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://heritage.scotsman.com/beltanefirefestival/Turning-up-the-heat-for.3278000.jp |title=Beltane festival |access-date=2011-01-01 |archive-date=2011-06-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110605102859/http://heritage.scotsman.com/beltanefirefestival/Turning-up-the-heat-for.3278000.jp |dead-url=no }}</ref>。每年十月初，印度教达瑟拉节（Dussehra）也在卡尔顿山庆祝<ref>McEwan, Allen, [http://edinburghnews.scotsman.com/evening-news-video-archive/Festival-is-flaming-marvellous.4560948.jp Festival is flaming marvellous] {{Wayback|url=http://edinburghnews.scotsman.com/evening-news-video-archive/Festival-is-flaming-marvellous.4560948.jp |date=20110821051814 }},Edinburgh Evening News, 2008-10-06, Accessed 2009-09-02</ref>。

